{
  "stem": "1918.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they sent into my ghetto, into my little area, a 16-year-old SS with a silver pistol, a German shepherd, a whip, and he called out the names-- we had to gather in the courtyard-- and called out the names that were originally compiled by the Judenrat, I guess.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Jewish council.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They sent out name collectors to every single Jewish home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So there was no escape.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The names were there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, and we had to line up, and here was a group.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And as he called the names, they had to go into the other group.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he called my mother's name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And just for good measure, he whipped her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my brother wanted to tear him apart.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my sisters and I, standing next to my brother, stepped on his foot and held down his arms not to let him kill the German-- try to kill him.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because we knew, in seconds we learned, a whole lifetime of tragedy, and realized that he, he will create a pool of blood.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He will slaughter my mother in front of our eyes, my brother.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he will not-- he will only create a pool of blood.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He will not kill all of us, and we'll have to watch there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then out of life [? is an ?] out of life, so let's go for it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we prevented him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he looked at us in such disbelief.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He couldn't believe, I am not allowed to kill somebody who hits my mother?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that very same brother of mine, the following morning when we were being deported, had, because he was very active in the ghetto-- he did all kinds of things that he could to help the, the Jews.",
      "word_count": 38
    }
  ],
